On today’s show, Emily is taking your calls, and giving you sure-fire ways to take your sex life and your relationships to the next level.

She gives you some ways to take your hand jobs to legendary status, reveals what people are really using tinder for, and how many people are getting it on at music festivals and where they’re doing it. Plus, she helps callers get relaxed for anal play, compromise when it comes to how long sex is lasting and how much sex is happening.
